project_descr:
Improving Rural Development in Georgia (ENPARD III)
Objective: promote inclusive/sustainable growth, creating employment & livelihoods for the poor and excluded; improvement of inst. capacities for implementation of Rural Development Strategy.

outputs.output_descr: Results: Improved governance for effective implementation of the National Rural Development Strategy, improved rural economic diversification, employment and services; Improved environment, sustainable management of natural resources and climate action.
